Lloyds, RBS Among Lenders to Take 5% Stake in HMV, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-06T20:46:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/lloyds-rbs-among-lenders-to-take-5-stake-in-hmv-sky-says.html
Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY) ,  Royal Bank
of Scotland Group Plc (RBS) ,  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  and other banks in  HMV
Group Plc (HMV) ’s lending syndicate, will take a 5 percent stake in
the entertainment retailer as part of a reorganization agreement
to be announced through the London Stock Exchange tomorrow, Sky
News reported, without saying where it got the information.  RBS spokesman Andy Cameron-Smith said he wasn’t in a
position to comment when contacted by telephone. Lloyds
spokesman Emile Abu-Shakra declined to comment as did an HMV
Group spokesman contacted by telephone outside office hours.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 